OL,3,CFamily calling for harsher punishment
OL,4,Cfor dangerous drivers after son killed
OL,6,FA mum is calling for harsher
OL,7,Fpunishments for people who cause death
OL,8,Fby dangerous driving, following the
OL,9,Fdeath of her 14-year old son.
OL,11,FRyan-Liam Morgan, 14, from Morecambe,
OL,12,Fdied in a crash just off the M6 in
OL,13,FApril 2025. He was being driven by his
OL,14,Fown father, Daniel Burba, who had
OL,15,Ftaken cocaine before having an
OL,16,Fepileptic episode at the wheel.
