OL,3,CFamily calling for harsher punishment
OL,4,Cfor dangerous drivers after son killed
OL,6,FSpeaking on Kim's behalf, Ryan-Liam's
OL,7,Fgrandmother Ann Bell said: "Like a
OL,8,Fblack clouds hanging over us, it's
OL,9,Fbeen awful. And we're struggling from
OL,10,Fday to day as it comes, you know? I
OL,11,Fmean, it's always in our thoughts.
OL,12,FAlways.
OL,14,F"We're fighting for him. We want
OL,15,Fjustice for him and everything. So
OL,16,Fbecause we think he deserves this."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
