OL,3,CFamily calling for harsher punishment
OL,4,Cfor dangerous drivers after son killed
OL,6,FThe family are advocating for "Ryan's
OL,7,FLaw", which would ensure a person who
OL,8,Fis guilty of killing someone by
OL,9,Fdriving recklessly, they would get a
OL,10,Flong sentence.
OL,12,FAnn said: "If they're under the
OL,13,Finfluence of drugs and alcohol and
OL,14,Fthey go driving recklessly and they
OL,15,Fkill someone, I don't see why they
OL,16,Fshould get a lenient sentence.
OL,18,F"They should get a really strong, long
OL,19,Fsentence. What they've done killing
OL,20,Fsomeone under the influence."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
