OL,3,CFamily calling for harsher punishment
OL,4,Cfor dangerous drivers after son killed
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,7,Fthe court when Daniel Burba was
OL,8,Fsentenced, Ryan-Liam's mum said her
OL,9,Fson had so much to live for.
OL,11,FShe said: "Not only did he take my
OL,12,Fboy's life, he took my boy's future."
OL,14,FA spokesperson from The Ministry of
OL,15,FJustice said "This was a terrible
OL,16,Fcrime and our thoughts remain with the
OL,17,Ffamily and friends of Ryan Morgan.
OL,18,FDangerous driving destroys lives and
OL,19,Fthe maximum penalty for causing death
OL,20,Fthrough this offence is life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
